<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>회원가입 완료</title>
  <meta http-equiv="refresh" content="3; url=/" />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff7f0, #ffe4e1);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      height: 100vh;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .message-box {
      background: white;
      padding: 2rem 3rem;
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .message-box h2 {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: #333;
    }

    .countdown {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-top: 1rem;
      color: #888;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="message-box">
    <h2>회원가입이 완료되었습니다!</h2>
    <p>이제 로그인하실 수 있어요.</p>
    <div class="countdown">홈페이지로 이동 중... <span id="seconds">3</span>초</div>
  </div>

  <script>
    let seconds = 3;
    const countdown = document.getElementById('seconds');

    const interval = setInterval(() => {
      seconds--;
      countdown.textContent = seconds;
      if (seconds <= 0) {
        clearInterval(interval);
      }
    }, 1000);
  </script>
</body>
</html>
